Class Bus

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iliashenko.Bus
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NotifierBus, java.lang.Runnable

    public class Bus
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable, NotifierBus
    Class that represent's bus entity. Every bus is thread and notifier for dispatcher observer. It notify observer on every stop.
